==Test Vectors==

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Script !! nLockTime !! nSequence !! Result
|-
| <100> CLTV DROP <pk> CHECKSIG || 100 || 0 || Valid
|-
| <100> CLTV DROP <pk> CHECKSIG || 99 || 0 || Invalid (locktime too low)
|-
| <100> CLTV DROP <pk> CHECKSIG || 100 || 0xffffffff || Invalid (sequence disables locktime)
|-
| <500000001> CLTV DROP <pk> CHECKSIG || 100 || 0 || Invalid (type mismatch)
|}

